def make_labels(df, n_neighbors, random_state, eps=0.5, min_samples=5):
    
    #U-mapで二次元に圧縮
    mapper = umap.UMAP(random_state=random_state, n_neighbors=n_neighbors)
    embedding = mapper.fit_transform(df.iloc[:,1:])
    
    #DBSCANでクラスタリング("eps"は任意)
    db = DBSCAN(eps=eps, min_samples=min_samples).fit(embedding)
    #label情報をデータフレームに追加
    labels = db.labels_
    
    return labels


def umap_plot(df, n_neighbors, random_state, eps=0.5, min_samples=5, figsize=(5,5), legend=False, ax=None):
    
    #U-mapで二次元に圧縮
    mapper = umap.UMAP(random_state=random_state, n_neighbors=n_neighbors)
    embedding = mapper.fit_transform(df.iloc[:,1:])

    #seabornで描画しやすいようにデータフレームに変換
    X_df = pd.concat([df["ID"], pd.DataFrame(embedding, columns=["x","y"])], axis=1)

    #DBSCANでクラスタリング("eps"は任意)
    db = DBSCAN(eps=eps, min_samples=min_samples).fit(embedding)
    #label情報をデータフレームに追加
    labels = db.labels_
    X_df["labels"] = labels

    #圧縮された要素を二次元に描画
    sns.scatterplot(data=X_df, x="x", y="y", hue="labels", palette="bright", ax=ax, legend=legend)


def trial_neighbors(df, n_neighbors, random_state=0, eps=0.5, min_samples=5, figsize=(15,5), figcol=3):
    
    figrow = math.ceil(len(n_neighbors)/figcol)
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figrow, figcol, figsize=figsize, tight_layout=True)
    
    for i, nn in enumerate(n_neighbors):
    
        #圧縮された要素を二次元に描画
        if figrow == 1: pltax = ax[i]
        else: pltax = ax[i//figcol, i%figcol]
        umap_plot(df, n_neighbors=nn, random_state=random_state, eps=eps, min_samples=min_samples, ax=pltax)
        pltax.set_title(f"n_neighbors:{nn}")
    
    plt.show()
    
    
def detect_knee(df, nearestN=5, umapN=5, pipeline=False, random_state=0, figsize=(8,4), umap_mins=10, S=1, legend=False, distance_col=-1):
    
    #U-mapで二次元に圧縮
    mapper = umap.UMAP(random_state=random_state, n_neighbors=umapN)
    embedding = mapper.fit_transform(df.iloc[:,1:])
    
    #距離を計算
    nearest_neighbors = NearestNeighbors(n_neighbors=nearestN)
    nearest_neighbors.fit(embedding)
    distances, indices = nearest_neighbors.kneighbors(embedding)
    if distance_col == -1: distance_col = nearestN-1
    distances = np.sort(distances, axis=0)[:, distance_col]
    
    #kneeを計算
    i = np.arange(len(distances))
    knee = KneeLocator(i, distances, S=S, curve='convex', direction='increasing', interp_method='polynomial')
    print(knee.knee_y)
    
    #描画領域
    if pipeline: fig, ax = plt.subplots(1,2, figsize=figsize, tight_layout=True)
    else: fig, ax = plt.subplots(1,1, figsize=figsize, tight_layout=True)
    
    if pipeline:

        #圧縮された要素を二次元に描画
        ax_scatter = ax[1]
        umap_plot(df, n_neighbors=umapN, eps=knee.knee_y, legend=legend, random_state=random_state, ax=ax_scatter, min_samples=umap_mins)
        ax_scatter.set_title(f"n_neighbors:{umapN}")
        
    #kneeの描画
    ax_knee = ax[0]
    sns.lineplot(x=knee.x, y=knee.y, ax=ax_knee)
    ax_knee.vlines(x=knee.knee, ymin=0, ymax=knee.y[-1], linestyles="--", colors="black")
    ax_knee.hlines(y=knee.knee_y, xmin=0, xmax=knee.x[-1], linestyles="--", colors="black")
    ax_knee.set_xlabel("Points")
    ax_knee.set_ylabel("Distance")
        
    plt.show()
    
    return knee

def cluster_heat(data, cls_col="cluster", figcol=3, figsize=(10, 5), tight=True, sharey="all", sharex="all"):
    
    #rowの必要数を計算
    uniques = data[cls_col].unique()
    n_cluster = uniques.shape[0]
    figrow = math.ceil(n_cluster/figcol)
    
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figrow, figcol, figsize=figsize, tight_layout=True, sharey=sharey, sharex=sharex)
    for i, cluster in enumerate(uniques):
        if figrow == 1: pltax = ax[i]
        else: pltax = ax[i//figrow, i%figcol]
        
        q = data.query(f"{cls_col} == {cluster}")
        sns.heatmap(q.iloc[:,1:-1], ax=pltax, cbar=False, vmin=0, vmax=1, cmap="Blues", center=0, xticklabels=False, yticklabels=False)
        pltax.set_title(f"cluster: {i} (n={q.shape[0]})")
        
    plt.show()
